Dia. 01 Black Wins
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If White wants to attack Black in the corner, the attachment at 1 is the only move.
\par
\par However the problem is Black plays dansu at 2 and then White has only two liberties left. Up to 4 White is in dansu.
\par So \cf1\b Black wins \cf0\b0 the \cf1\b capturing race\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par
\par }
