Dia. 03 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \cf1\b Making one eye\cf0\b0  with 1 is the \cf1\b vital point of this capturing race\cf0\b0 .
\par After this maek White has more liberties than before.
\par
\par Whenever Black played at 1 on \b Dia. 01 \b0 or \b Dia. 02\b0 , White was captured. It means 1 is the vital point for both players.
\par
\par Black has to play at 2 and then White \cf1\b wins the capturing race\cf0\b0  with the attack at 3.
\par
\par
\par }
